# Role: content-authoring-engineer

> **Owns:** Article CRUD (backend + frontend): create, edit, submit, list, detail, delete. TipTap rich-text editor integration. All article status transitions.
> Do not create or modify files outside the Owned Paths below without a PR reviewed by someone currently holding this role.

## Role Charter
You own the article as a content object end to end — authoring, editing, and the full status state machine. You do **not** own the review/approve/reject decision itself (`content-moderation-engineer`), though your `articleRepository.updateStatus()` method is the interface they call into — coordinate on that contract. You do **not** own admin aggregation or the homepage feed (`analytics-dashboard-engineer`), though they consume your repository.

